### ==========================================================================
### CSA-in-a-Box — APIM Gateway Endpoint Tests
### VS Code REST Client format (humao.rest-client extension)
### ==========================================================================

### Variables
@apimUrl = https://csa-datamesh-apim-gw-dev-XXXXXX.azure-api.us
@subscriptionKey = your-subscription-key-here
@accessToken = your-jwt-access-token-here

### ==========================================================================
### DAB — Data API Builder (REST + GraphQL)
### ==========================================================================

### GET Data Products via DAB REST
GET {{apimUrl}}/dab/api/DataProducts
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{subscriptionKey}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### GET single Data Product by ID
GET {{apimUrl}}/dab/api/DataProducts/id/1
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{subscriptionKey}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### DAB GraphQL query
POST {{apimUrl}}/dab/graphql
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{subscriptionKey}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "query": "{ dataProducts(first: 10) { items { id name domain qualityScore } } }"
}

### ==========================================================================
### AI Services
### ==========================================================================

### Chat completion
POST {{apimUrl}}/ai/api/v1/ai/chat
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{subscriptionKey}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "messages": [
        { "role": "user", "content": "What data products are available in the finance domain?" }
    ],
    "max_tokens": 500
}

###

### Generate embeddings
POST {{apimUrl}}/ai/api/v1/ai/embed
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{subscriptionKey}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "text": "quarterly revenue report financial data",
    "model": "text-embedding-ada-002"
}

### ==========================================================================
### Marketplace
### ==========================================================================

### List all data products in marketplace
GET {{apimUrl}}/marketplace/api/v1/marketplace/products
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{subscriptionKey}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Search products by domain
GET {{apimUrl}}/marketplace/api/v1/marketplace/products?domain=finance&search=revenue
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{subscriptionKey}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### List domains
GET {{apimUrl}}/marketplace/api/v1/marketplace/domains
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{subscriptionKey}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Request access to a data product
POST {{apimUrl}}/marketplace/api/v1/marketplace/access-requests
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{subscriptionKey}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "productId": "prod-001",
    "justification": "Need finance data for quarterly report automation",
    "requestedRole": "reader"
}

### ==========================================================================
### Portal Core API
### ==========================================================================

### Get current user profile
GET {{apimUrl}}/portal/api/v1/users/me
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{subscriptionKey}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### List governance policies
GET {{apimUrl}}/portal/api/v1/governance/policies
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{subscriptionKey}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ==========================================================================
### Error Cases — Testing auth and rate limits
### ==========================================================================

### Missing subscription key (expect 401)
GET {{apimUrl}}/dab/api/DataProducts
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Missing JWT (expect 401)
GET {{apimUrl}}/dab/api/DataProducts
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{subscriptionKey}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Invalid JWT (expect 401)
GET {{apimUrl}}/dab/api/DataProducts
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{subscriptionKey}}
Authorization: Bearer invalid-token-here
Accept: application/json

###

### Rate limit test — run rapidly to trigger 429
# @name rateLimitTest
GET {{apimUrl}}/ai/api/v1/ai/chat
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{subscriptionKey}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json
